Notes:

Box - Sizing:

Content-box
button 122

border-box
button 100

button {
width:100px;
padding:10px;
border: 1px solid black
}

* {
box-sizing: border-box;
}

Position: fixed --> width is determined by content
or
absolute --> unlocks top, right, bottom, left, z-index

overlay:
section {
position:fixed;
top:0;
bottom:0;
right:0;
left:0;
}

Tables:
<table>
Each row - <tr>
Each column - <td>
</table>

cells go within rows, everything goes within a <table> tag
Optional:
  <thead> - header row
  <th> - like TD but for a header

<td colspan="2">  if you want to merge cells

CSS Classes:
Re-use CSS rules without the need for an element
Rule--> named
Custom adjective

Use a dot "." to select 
